Feature: TC_07_STAFF - SIM Amendments and History Tab E2E Regression Pack

  Background:
    Given user on staff login page
    When Staff logs in with the Username "agr4442"
    And Staff opens the "Basic Income Support for Sustainability" application

  @regression @staff @sim @history @e2e
  Scenario: AT-STAFF-SIM-E2E-01 - Staff performs SIM parcel amendments and verifies history activity

    # SECTION 1 : Open submitted herd application - AT-TC-01 (BISSAGL-14998)
    When Staff searches on the Home screen with the following details
      | field      | herdNumber |
      | herdValue  | G175C038   |
      | schemeYear | 2023       |
    And Staff clicks the "View" link number 1 in the "application-search-table" table
    Then Staff clicks on "SIM" Link in Navbar

    # SECTION 2 : Amend SIM found area on a parcel + verify history
    When Staff opens the SIM parcel "G17202130" side drawer
    And Staff enters value "4" in the "simFoundArea" SIM side drawer field
    And Staff clicks the "Save changes" button
    Then Staff clicks on "Notes/History" Link in Navbar
    And Staff switches to the "History" tab
    Then Staff verifies the History tab shows activity

    # SECTION 3 : Amend SIM claimed area on a parcel + verify history
    When Staff clicks on "SIM" Link in Navbar
    And Staff opens the SIM parcel "G22814025" side drawer
    And Staff enters value "6" in the "amendedClaimedArea" SIM side drawer field
    And Staff clicks the "Save changes" button
    Then Staff clicks on "Notes/History" Link in Navbar
    And Staff switches to the "History" tab
    Then Staff verifies the History tab shows activity

    # SECTION 4 : Toggle SIM indicator on a parcel + verify history
    When Staff clicks on "SIM" Link in Navbar
    And Staff opens the SIM parcel "G22813057" side drawer
    And Staff clicks the "simIndicator" checkbox in the SIM parcel edit drawer
    And Staff clicks the "Save changes" button
    Then Staff clicks on "Notes/History" Link in Navbar
    And Staff switches to the "History" tab
    Then Staff verifies the History tab shows activity

    # SECTION 5 : Submit SIM and confirm, then verify history
    When Staff clicks on "SIM" Link in Navbar
    And Staff clicks the "Submit" button
    And Staff enters SIM notes as "Test 7678"
    And Staff clicks the "Finish" button
    And Staff toggles the SIM option
    Then Staff clicks on "Notes/History" Link in Navbar
    And Staff switches to the "History" tab
    Then Staff verifies the History tab shows activity

    # SECTION 6 : Revert SIM back to original state (post-test reset)
    When Staff clicks on "SIM" Link in Navbar
    And Staff toggles the SIM option
    Then Staff clicks on "Notes/History" Link in Navbar
    And Staff switches to the "History" tab
    Then Staff verifies the History tab shows activity
    When Staff clicks on "SIM" Link in Navbar
